<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Concerto: Open Source Digital Signage</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="main-nav">

    <div class="content">

      <div class="pure-menu pure-menu-open pure-menu-horizontal">
        <%= link_to page_path("overview"), class: "pure-menu-heading" do %><%= image_tag("ConcertoLogo_main-nav.png", :alt => "Concerto", :width => 200) %><% end %>

        <ul>
          <li><%= link_to :controller => :pages, :action => :show, :id => "demo" do %><b>Try</b> Concerto<% end %></li>
          <li><%= link_to :controller => :pages, :action => :show, :id => "deploy" do %><b>Deploy</b> Concerto<% end %></li>
          <li><%= link_to :controller => :pages, :action => :list_help do %>Get <b>Help</b><% end %></li>
          <li><%= link_to :controller => :pages, :action => :list_blog do %><b>Blog</b><% end %></li>
          <li><a href="http://groups.google.com/group/concerto-digital-signage"><b>Forum</b></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <%= link_to "v1", :controller => :pages, :action => :show, :id => "v1" %>
      <%= link_to "v1 Help", :controller => :pages, :action => :list_v1help %>

      <div id="user_nav">
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          Signed in as <%= current_user.name %>. Not you?
          <%= link_to "Sign out", destroy_user_session_path %>
        <% else %> 
          <%= link_to "Sign in", user_omniauth_authorize_path(:google_oauth2) %>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

<div class="content">
  <%= yield %>

  <br />

  <h1>What if I Need Help?</h1>

  <br />

  <h1>Header One</h1>
  <h2>Header Two</h2>
  <h3>Header Three</h3>
  <h4>Header Four</h4>
  <h5>Header Five</h5>
  <h6>Header Six</h6>

  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse et vulputate purus, vitae tincidunt ante. Maecenas tincidunt, magna at varius varius, enim justo imperdiet eros, et lacinia orci diam sit amet dolor. Cras aliquam dui mauris, et fermentum dui fringilla nec.</p>

  <a href="#" title="">Link tag illustration</a>
</div>


</body>
</html>
